# Minimal RFC 2865 RADIUS dictionary — just the standard attributes the
# NetPulse health check sends in an Access-Request. pyrad needs attribute
# definitions to encode a packet; an empty Dictionary() cannot.
ATTRIBUTE	User-Name		1	string
ATTRIBUTE	User-Password		2	octets
ATTRIBUTE	NAS-IP-Address		4	ipaddr
ATTRIBUTE	NAS-Port		5	integer
ATTRIBUTE	Service-Type		6	integer
ATTRIBUTE	NAS-Identifier		32	string
